extendedInfo.description: GO Contacts Industrial Theme! Your GO Contacts will never look the same. You'll get the feeling of metal, clay and everything "industrial" after installing this theme. Read on for the most important elements:* This Theme Will NOT install any sort of ads on your phone.* Part of the Industrial Design Series, so you'll love the feeling you get when browsing around in the Contacts.* Perfect 5 Star Rating.* Transitions, dials and animations all custom made.GET THE THEME NOW, NO NEED TO WAIT!This Contacts theme is not standalone app, you need to download the latest version of GO Contacts EXTo apply the theme from GO Contacts: Menu->Theme.We had so much fun developing this particular theme. Creating the icons, the wallpapers, testing it on different devices, the experience was great. We only hope you'll find it as awesome as we do. Send us your thoughts via e-mail or through comments and ratings. Be sure we respond to each and every user and are glad to read every comment.Contact Us: (we would love to hear from you)www.studio4apps.comstudio4apps@gmail.comfacebook.com/Studio4Appstwitter.com/Studio4Appps
